data.description: Adorable One Story Villa, this is a 3/2 w/ Garage. It features a Foyer Entrance, Large Eat-in-Kitchen with White Wood Cabinets, New Stainless Steel Appliances, Pantry, Recessed Lights. Ceramic Tile throughout; New Paint. Master Bedroom with Large Walk in Closet, Master Bathroom with Roman Tub and Shower. New Washer & dryer in 2022. Property will have a Brand New AC System prior to Closing. New Roof & Gutters 2019. Enjoy the Long and Serene Garden View from the Extended, Roofed and Screened Patio. HOA covers Cable, Internet, Ext. Insurance. Gated Community 24 hrs, it offers Pools, Clubhouses, Gym, Hot Tub, Playgrounds, Basketball, Volleyball, Tennis & Pickleball Courts. Excellent location, Great Schools, Close to Everything!!!
